Write a program to find the sum of digits of a number until the sum becomes a single digit.
Input Format
Input format consists of a number
Output Format
Output format consists of an integer
Sample Input 0
8945623
Sample Output 0
8
Case 1
Case 2
Input (stdin)
78945623
Output (stdout)
8

program

n = int(input( ))
while n >= 10:
    digit = 0
    while n > 0:
        digit += n % 10
        n //= 10
    n = digit
print(n)
